heading: Garan Hold Dungeon Guide
content: Garan Hold contains a fantastic Barbarian aspect, the . The monster families here are quite poor, and make the dungeon overall slow to complete. Look elsewhere for excellent XP or Nightmare Dungeon speed. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
